OL,3,CPSNI officer appears in court accused
OL,4,Cof ammunition theft
OL,6,FA police officer has appeared in court
OL,7,Faccused of stealing ammunition and
OL,8,Fabusing his position of trust within
OL,9,Fthe PSNI.
OL,11,FRodgers, whose address was given as
OL,12,FPSNI Brooklyn, Knock Road in Belfast,
OL,13,Ffaces eight charges relating to the
OL,14,Falleged theft of ammunition from the
OL,15,FPSNI Steeple training facility.
OL,17,FAppearing at Antrim Magistrates Court,
OL,18,Fsitting in Ballymena, 63-year-old
OL,19,FRobert Charles Rodgers confirmed he
OL,20,Funderstood the charges against him.
