OL,6,FThe 63-year-old is also charged with
OL,7,Fthe theft of ammunition "on a date
OL,8,Funtil 7 October 2025," in addition to
OL,9,Fan accusation of fraud by abuse of
OL,10,Fposition on 27 July this year.
OL,12,FThe officer is understood to have been
OL,13,Fsuspended pending the outcome of the
OL,14,Fcriminal proceedings,
